      <body>
         <div>
            <div>
               <p rend="center"><hi rend="superscript">Open</hi> Letter to any writer of any article
                     <lb/>“<rs type="periodical" key="J54">Portugal</rs>” in any
                  Encyclo<pc>-</pc><lb/>pedia<lb/> with some hints to the writers<lb/> of <seg
                     type="anchor"><add place="above" n="2">a few other</add> correlated</seg>
                  articles</p>
            </div>
            <metamark rend="line center" function="distinct"/>
            <div>
               <p rend="center"><choice>
                     <abbr>Re<am>.</am></abbr>
                     <expan>Re<ex>spond</ex></expan>
                  </choice> to the sociological errors <choice>
                     <abbr>&amp;</abbr>
                     <expan>and</expan>
                  </choice> injustices done to Portugal by the<lb/> generality of writers on <del
                     rend="overstrike">the</del> it <note place="margin-right" n="2">√</note></p>
            </div>
            <metamark rend="line" function="distinct"/>
            <div>
               <p rend="center">Scotland in general and Burns<lb/> in particular. <note
                     place="margin-right" n="2">X</note></p>
            </div>
            <metamark rend="line" function="distinct"/>
            <div>
               <head rend="center"><hi rend="underline">An Ointment for Burns.</hi></head>
               <p rend="center">Being a critical analysis of the<lb/> poetry of Robert of that <lb/>
                  <hi rend="framed"><seg type="anchor"><add place="above" n="2">ending</add>
                        surname</seg></hi>. <note place="margin-right" rend="circled" n="2"
                  >√</note></p>
            </div>
            <metamark rend="line" function="distinct"/>
            <div>
               <head rend="center">
                  <metamark rend="arrow-down" function="assignment" target="#A1"/>
                  <hi rend="underline"><rs type="periodical" key="J55">The New Decadence</rs></hi>
               </head>
               <p rend="center">An Introduction to the Study of <lb/>Indifference.</p>
            </div>
            <metamark rend="line center" function="distinct"/>
            <div>
               <p rend="center">
                  <anchor xml:id="A1"/>
                  <hi rend="circled">or</hi> Being an apology <subst>
                     <add n="2" place="above">for</add>
                     <del n="1">of</del>
                  </subst> all culture not genuine. </p>
            </div>
         </div>
